data.description: Welcome to this delightful home situated in the Westwood community! This charming residence, built by Clayton Homes, features a concrete foundation, no HOA fees, a corner lot, and an attached garage. It offers the ideal blend of city convenience and the peacefulness of small-town living, just an hour away from the city. Inside, you'll find exquisite laminate flooring and a modern kitchen that are sure to make a memorable impression.
